column1: # Title: Mapping of SUA items to their item_code
# Description: Ideally we just use SUA (supply utilization accounts) item names directly.  However
# it helps to use item_code to reduce the size of the input data as well as speed up processing.  We will then need this mapping
# to ultimately translate back to item names. TM is TRUE when bilateral data was used for the item.
Milk, products of natural constituents nes
